    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In our game, you will step into the shoes of a supermarket worker — and trust us, it’s anything but boring! Serve customers at the checkout, adjust prices, unload and stock the shelves, decorate your store and even your own apartment. Increase your reputation, and always remember: somewhere nearby a sneaky thief or a strict inspector might be lurking. And she doesn’t forgive mistakes!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3279570/extras/a1e57b7a402319d361367dedad9800bc.avif?t=1767850509\" width=800 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Order goods and place them on the shelves. Don’t forget to set the price and keep your stock up to date. Remember: the more happy customers you have, the more profit you earn!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3279570/extras/077f39a25cce5f9e2c76e3f674253c61.poster.avif?t=1767850509\" width=1000 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3279570/extras/077f39a25cce5f9e2c76e3f674253c61.webm?t=1767850509\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3279570/extras/077f39a25cce5f9e2c76e3f674253c61.mp4?t=1767850509\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3279570/extras/131096d7bfec967d5088cef71a5e132c.avif?t=1767850509\" width=800 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play solo or team up with up to four players. Share the roles among yourselves, because teamwork is the key to success. P.S. But sometimes it’s just fun to unleash a little chaos! :)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3279570/extras/02d4d8f5cb3a1c4162b280e17c4780cf.poster.avif?t=1767850509\" width=1000 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3279570/extras/02d4d8f5cb3a1c4162b280e17c4780cf.webm?t=1767850509\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3279570/extras/02d4d8f5cb3a1c4162b280e17c4780cf.mp4?t=1767850509\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3279570/extras/5a804af7056c4ea252815fce4d47baa3.avif?t=1767850509\" width=800 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Customize your character’s appearance, design your store, and furnish your apartment just the way you like. Everything depends only on your imagination!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3279570/extras/ba089fb63bcb565098a2d5d1b3e3267c.poster.avif?t=1767850509\" width=1000 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3279570/extras/ba089fb63bcb565098a2d5d1b3e3267c.webm?t=1767850509\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3279570/extras/ba089fb63bcb565098a2d5d1b3e3267c.mp4?t=1767850509\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
